{
  "texts": [
    "The RGB images were taken at 30 FPS, 8-bit and 1280 × 720 dimensions.",
    "Thermal and depth maps were projected onto the RGB images from thermal and depth cameras.",
    "The camera box containing the thermal camera, an Android smartphone, and the depth camera was attached to the back of a computer laptop, where the wound image capture was done with one click simultaneously from the laptop.",
    "Wound images were taken within a 1-2 feet distance between the surface of the wound and the front of the box where the camera lenses were located.",
    "Data collectionTo select eligible participants for this dataset, we used the following inclusion and exclusion criteria."
  ]
}